            Once in a blue moon, I blog about statistics and machine
            learning. I am fortunate: one of my passions is also my day
            job. That said, all opinions here are, of course, my own.
            Now and again, to keep you on your tippy toes, I might write
            about other things. By the way, I’m Vathy M. Kamulete and
            @vathymut on
            most social platforms.
